{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回　再入江湖：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第五回再入江湖四年，好像在一晃眼间就过去了。熊倜跟着飘然老人，隐居在泰山，已经苦练了四年的武功了。四年，江湖上起了很大的变化。江南第一的江宁府鸣远镖局瓦解了，金陵三杰中的断魂剑与神刀霸王已不知去向。峨嵋的孤峰一剑边浩，自峨嵋绝顶，巧得失传已久的\"玄女剑法\"秘笈，成了江湖上数一数二的剑客，和江苏虎丘飞灵堡的出尘剑客东方灵，被武林中人并称\"章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位可是来英雄会的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是应该如此，我们还是免了这些虚套最好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我尽管和你们说话，却把外面的客人都忘了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让他们等等好了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们自去无妨，我陪家姐在这里坐好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南偌大个地方，难道其中竟没有藏龙卧虎……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道此人又与天阴教有什么关联吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎地子母金梭武大侠来了，我都不知道，真是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_zi_ubgkz",
      "speaker_name": "汉子喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锁喉穴",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好朋友要动手就动手，别多废话。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你轻功如此好，只怕……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这多么像她说话的声音呀，那么地轻巧而缓慢……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "东方灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实他们早走了，只不过我在外面想着一件事……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还讲，你不是笑我，是笑谁呀？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只当这房子里就只有你一个才好笑呀。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我说给你们听，从前有一个人呀……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这人怎么搞的，一会儿拍桌子，一会又笑了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道又是那人儿……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别走，你过来，我问你几句话。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你过来不过来？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狂又怎地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "舵主，这个就是叫熊倜的小子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘请了，在下和姑娘素昧生平，姑娘竟插手相助，在下确是感激……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 842,
      "line_end": 842
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看这小子愣头愣脑，却不料他竟有如此佳人相伴……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 864,
      "line_end": 864
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好，想不到今日竟然有向我孤峰一剑边某人叫阵的人，而且居然是个女子，我边浩行走江湖多年，真还没有和女子交过手，可是，今日么……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小生熊倜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 902,
      "line_end": 902
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我知道你不告诉我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我刚才放在桌上的两个包袱，你可见到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 964,
      "line_end": 964
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有，没有。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别看着我，有什么事尽管说好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1046,
      "line_end": 1046
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不认识我了，可是我却认识你呢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1048,
      "line_end": 1048
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你大年初一的清早，不也跑到这里来了吗！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是……只是你穿得这么少，岂不要冻坏了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1076,
      "line_end": 1076
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一点也不冷呀。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1078
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时我真恨你，那时我叫你陪着我，你为什么不肯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1098,
      "line_end": 1098
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是我呀，我就去抢了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1112,
      "line_end": 1112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自若馨死后，本来已觉得心如死灰了，可是不知怎么回事，我看到了她只觉得高兴得很，只想跟她在一块儿，别的事全想不起了……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1124,
      "line_end": 1124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在想着你，我看到了你，心里就高兴得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1130,
      "line_end": 1130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1132,
      "line_end": 1132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也喜欢它吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1154,
      "line_end": 1154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1156,
      "line_end": 1156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有马场？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1162,
      "line_end": 1162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你喜欢的，我都会喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1168
    }
  ],
